# I18n Labels

- Never hardcode labels or user-facing text in HTML templates or TypeScript.
- Store new UI text in `it.json` using the existing translation key structure.
- Reference labels through the project translation mechanism, not inline strings.
- When editing existing text, update the translation key/value instead of duplicating hardcoded copy.
- For i18n-heavy changes, read `.cursor/skills/i18n-labels/SKILL.md`.
